  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GlobalUsageGenerator<T>
    Deprecated. 
    The RONN format has some know bugs and it is recommended to use classes from the airline-help-man or airline-help-markdown modules instead of classes from this module

    @Deprecated
public class RonnMultiPageGlobalUsageGenerator<T>
extends RonnGlobalUsageGenerator<T>
    A global usage generator that creates a top level overview man page (a la git) and generates separate man pages for each command provided by the CLI. The top level man page references the other man pages using proper man page style references that RONN will recognise and handle appropriately.

    The overview man page will be generated to the provided output stream BUT new files are generated in the working directory for the individual command man pages

    Author:
    rvesse
